Silvercorp Metals Inc.


            
            Silvercorp Metals, Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, development and mining of precious and base metal properties in China and Canada. The company was founded by Rui Feng on October 31, 1991 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




