Silvercorp Metals (SVM) Shares Enter Oversold Territory
In trading on Wednesday, shares of Silvercorp Metals Inc entered into oversold territory, changing hands as low as $0.9317 per share. We define oversold territory using the Relative Strength Index, or RSI, which is a technical analysis indicator used to measure momentum on a scale of zero to 100.

